This allows funding schedules to adapt automatically as financial circumstances change.

Priority Engine

Not every bill carries the same importance.

The Priority Engine ranks financial obligations according to user preferences and predefined categories.

Example priority order:

Mortgage / Rent
Utilities
Insurance
Transportation
Debt Payments
Subscriptions
Entertainment

If income is lower than expected, the engine prioritizes essential obligations first.

Protected Digital Vaults

Each recurring expense is assigned its own protected vault.

Money allocated to a vault is visually separated from available spending funds while remaining fully transparent to the user.

Every vault tracks:

Target Amount
Current Balance
Funding Percentage
Due Date
Remaining Contributions
Estimated Completion Date
Funding Status

