Release Engine

Funds remain protected until their scheduled release.

Once the payment date arrives, the Release Engine authorizes payment according to user-defined preferences.

Possible release methods include:

Scheduled bank transfer
Bill payment
Debit authorization
Future banking integrations
Financial Readiness Score

